The application of AllSAT to domains like model checking and data mining suggests a connection to artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The study of symmetries in combinatorial structures is a topic in logic (cs.LO). The use of Boolean formulas to generate all possible edge colorings of a graph is a problem in computational complexity (cs.CC). Finally, the paper deals with the generation of complete sets of colorings, which is a topic in discrete structures (cs.DS).
